found it -- but at a hideous price. ','http://www.netflix.com/Movie/House_of_the_Dead/60031234','http://api.netflix.com/catalog/titles/movies/60031234/similars','2011-06-03 16:36:01','2011-06-03 16:36:01'),(151,1,'http://cdn-4.nflximg.com/us/boxshots/large/70041954.jpg','BloodRayne','2.8',2006,'http://api.netflix.com/catalog/titles/movies/70041954',94,'Bloodthirsty Lord Kagan (Ben Kingsley) wants his half-human, half vampire daughter to become a full-fledged vampiress, but fanged femme fatale Rayne (Kristanna Loken) denounces her father\'s legacy and instead joins up with a trio of vampire hunters (Michael Madsen, Michelle Rodriguez and Matt Davis). Billy Zane and Udo Kier co-star in this Gothic horror film based on the popular video game of the same name.','http://www.netflix.com/Movie/BloodRayne/70041954','http://api.netflix.com/catalog/titles/movies/70041954/similars','2011-06-03 16:37:07','2011-06-03 16:37:07'),(152,1,'http://cdn-4.nflximg.com/us/boxshots/large/70077124.jpg','BloodRayne 2: Deliverance','2.5',2007,'http://api.netflix.com/catalog/titles/movies/70077124',95,'Things get even wilder in the already Wild West when Billy the Kid (Zack Ward) and his band of cowboy buddies -- vampires one and all -- arrive in Deliverance, Mont., to establish their kingdom. Now, it\'s up to the half-human, half-vampire Rayne (Natassia Malthe) to use her fearsome powers to stop them. Along for the ride is reporter Newton Pyles (Chris Coppola), whom Billy spares so he can tell the bloodsuckers\' story.','http://www.netflix.com/Movie/BloodRayne_2_Deliverance/70077124','http://api.netflix.com/catalog/titles/movies/70077124/similars','2011-06-03 16:37:11','2011-06-03 16:37:11'),(153,1,'http://cdn-0.nflximg.com/us/boxshots/large/70181840.jpg','BloodRayne: The Third Reich','3.6',2010,'http://api.netflix.com/catalog/titles/movies/70181840',79,'In this action adventure spun off from a video game, half-human, half-vampire rebel spirit Rayne is pitted against a dark evil from another time -- a squad of undead Nazi warriors trying to inject Adolf Hitler with Rayne\'s blood to make him immortal.','http://www.netflix.com/Movie/BloodRayne_The_Third_Reich/70181840','http://api.netflix.com/catalog/titles/movies/70181840/similars','2011-06-03 16:37:14','2011-06-03 16:37:14'),(154,1,'http://cdn-4.nflximg.com/us/boxshots/large/70126924.jpg','Far Cry','2.8',2008,'http://api.netflix.com/catalog/titles/movies/70126924',95,'When Seattle reporter Valerie Cardinal (Emmanuelle Vaugier) hires troubled ex-commando Jack Carver (Til Schweiger) to guide her to a remote Pacific island, she soon falls prey to mercenaries sworn to protect the island\'s dark military secret. Now Carver must save Cardinal and confront the sinister Dr. Krieger (Udo Kier), whose biological experiments have gone wildly awry. Uwe Boll directs this action-thriller based on the popular video game.','http://www.netflix.com/Movie/Far_Cry/70126924','http://api.netflix.com/catalog/titles/movies/70126924/similars','2011-06-03 16:38:47','2011-06-03 16:38:47'),(155,1,'http://cdn-5.nflximg.com/us/boxshots/large/70135585.jpg','The Final Storm','2.9',2009,'http://api.netflix.com/catalog/titles/movies/70135585',85,'When a storm of apocalyptic force descends on their farm, husband and wife Tom (Steve Bacic) and Gillian (Lauren Holly) offer shelter to a mysterious stranger named Silas (Luke Perry) -- who then ends up offering protection to the couple and their son (Cole Heppell). As they strive to cope with the devastation around them, the family begins to realize that Silas may have brought with him a new type of danger in this Uwe Boll-helmed thriller. ','http://www.netflix.com/Movie/The_Final_Storm/70135585','http://api.netflix.com/catalog/titles/movies/70135585/similars','2011-06-03 16:39:31','2011-06-03 16:39:31');
